to assassinate me and Princess.

114
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:06,740
Speak.

115
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:08,909
What other schemes are you hiding?

116
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,159
Madam,

117
00:05:15,970 --> 00:05:18,100
