120
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:42,360
Your Highness,

121
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,220
this matter

122
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,300
was my doing alone.

123
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:50,760
It has nothing to do
with the Marquis of Zhenguo's Mansion.

124
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,420
Please,

125
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,960
