290
00:14:02,490 --> 00:14:03,410
An old friend.

291
00:14:03,690 --> 00:14:04,490
Old friend?

292
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,980
This is for you.

293
00:14:07,930 --> 00:14:09,110
While I'm away,

294
00:14:09,130 --> 00:14:11,190
you can use this to protect yourself.

295
00:14:15,610 --> 00:14:16,370
Remember,

296
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,230
hold it steady

297
00:14:17,850 --> 00:14:19,040
and aim at one spot.

298
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:20,920
I hit it!

299
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:26,220
Careful,

300
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:27,100
don't get wet.

301
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,110
Let me try again.

302
00:14:34,070 --> 00:14:35,640
It seems this old friend

303
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:37,480
means a lot to you.

304
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,640
Yes,

305
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
very much.

306
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,680
Good.

307
00:14:57,810 --> 00:14:58,610
By the way.

308
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,450
after Madam Cui's case,

309
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:03,710
Zhou's Mansion may no longer
be a suitable place for you.

310
00:15:03,710 --> 00:15:04,510
Princess,

311
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:05,970
why not change your residence?

312
00:15:05,970 --> 00:15:07,570
You'll be more comfortable.

313
00:15:08,210 --> 00:15:09,250
I won't leave.

314
00:15:09,460 --> 00:15:11,390
I have more important things to do.

315
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,280
What things?

316
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:14,620
I'd be glad to help.

317
00:15:16,130 --> 00:15:16,930
Prince Yan,

318
00:15:18,010 --> 00:15:20,070
I'm about to be arranged in marriage.

319
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:24,140
We should

320
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,650
keep our distance.

321
00:15:44,890 --> 00:15:47,420
The day of the marriage alliance
is approaching.

322
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:48,960
I need to make plans early.

323
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:52,710
Wait.

324
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,580
Your Highness.

325
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,490
What's that in your hand?

326
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:58,210
Your Highness,

327
00:15:58,210 --> 00:16:01,870
Lady Ruoxi sent me to deliver this letter
to the Prince's mansion.

328
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,200
[Letter to the Prince]

329
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:06,780
Xi wants to meet Prince Yan?

330
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:13,490
Your Highness.

331
00:16:14,250 --> 00:16:15,140
Miss Ruoxi.

332
00:16:18,580 --> 00:16:20,040
Why did you ask me

333
00:16:20,070 --> 00:16:20,950
here today?

334
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,520
Your Highness,

335
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,450
will you help me?

336
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:32,110
Could it be

337
00:16:32,490 --> 00:16:34,680
[Letter to the Prince]

338
00:16:32,970 --> 00:16:35,570
she's going to follow
the same path I once took?

339
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,570
Without entering reincarnation,

340
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:53,780
one must be reborn.

341
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:57,390
This dreamlike life will soon awaken,

342
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,240
and all things

343
00:17:01,010 --> 00:17:02,350
must come to an end.

344
00:17:03,970 --> 00:17:05,540
Same appearance,

345
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,010
but different fate.

346
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:10,070
Who exactly decides our fate?

347
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:12,830
I refuse to believe it.

348
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,610
Back in Yuzhou,

349
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:25,460
I could clearly feel
that she cared about me.

350
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:29,250
But why is she so distant now?

351
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,990
It's truly puzzling.

352
00:17:32,130 --> 00:17:32,720
Your Highness,

353
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:33,790
the carriage is ready.

354
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:37,050
Didn't Miss Zhou Ruoxi invite you
to meet by the Moon River?

355
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:38,810
Yes.

356
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:47,380
[Prince Yan's Mansion]

357
00:17:58,839 --> 00:17:59,800
Miss Ruoxi,

358
00:17:59,819 --> 00:18:00,720
didn't you invite me

359
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,119
to meet by the Moon River?

360
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:03,780
Why did you suddenly

361
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:06,220
come to my residence
for a game of chess instead?

362
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:07,750
Boating on the lake is dull.

363
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:09,380
It's much more enjoyable

364
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:11,480
to stay here playing chess
and drinking tea

365
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,640
with Your Highness.

366
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,720
Having known you for so long,

367
00:18:16,740 --> 00:18:17,740
I had no idea

368
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:19,570
you had such refined interests.

369
00:18:19,630 --> 00:18:21,030
I just learned recently.

370
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:22,390
Perfect opportunity to

371
00:18:22,390 --> 00:18:24,050
practice with Your Highness.

372
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:27,000
Your playing style

373
00:18:27,100 --> 00:18:28,260
doesn't seem like

374
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:29,940
that of a beginner.

375
00:18:30,700 --> 00:18:31,770
It rather has

376
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:33,660
the confidence of a chess master.

377
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:36,430
Are you giving up already, Your Highness?

378
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,300
Your Highness,

379
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:03,790
watch out for the encirclement below.

380
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,010
Miss Ruoxi, you understand me,

381
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:10,000
and likewise,

382
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:11,990
I understand you too.

383
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:18,180
Your Highness,
your reputation is well-deserved.

384
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:19,310
It's my honor to have

385
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,790
a worthy opponent like you.

386
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:21,450
Liang Feng,

387
00:19:21,850 --> 00:19:22,650
serve the tea.

388
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:26,520
Please.

389
00:19:33,630 --> 00:19:36,290
This peach kernel tea
is bitter and astringent.

390
00:19:36,490 --> 00:19:39,570
Only after getting used to it
can one tastes its sweetness.

391
00:19:39,570 --> 00:19:40,870
It's what Princess likes.

